AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <https://w3id.org/metpo/1000801> "Aerobic respiration")
SubClassOf(<https://w3id.org/metpo/1000801> <https://w3id.org/metpo/1000800>)

# Class: <https://w3id.org/metpo/1000802> (Anaerobic respiration)

