AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasRelatedSynonym> <https://w3id.org/metpo/1000802> "Anoxic respiration")
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasRelatedSynonym> <https://w3id.org/metpo/1000802> "Dissimilatory respiration (non-O₂)")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <https://w3id.org/metpo/1000802> "Anaerobic respiration")
SubClassOf(<https://w3id.org/metpo/1000802> <https://w3id.org/metpo/1000800>)

# Class: <https://w3id.org/metpo/1000803> (Oxidative phosphorylation)

