AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <https://w3id.org/metpo/1003004> "obligately alkaliphilic")
SubClassOf(<https://w3id.org/metpo/1003004> <https://w3id.org/metpo/1003002>)

# Class: <https://w3id.org/metpo/1003005> (facultatively alkaliphilic)

AnnotationAssertion(Annotation(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000119> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/MICRO_0001558>) Annotation(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000119> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OMP_0005009>) Annotation(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000119> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OMP_0005011>) Annotation(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000119> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OMP_0007771>) Annotation(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000119> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OMP_0007947>) <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <https://w3id.org/metpo/1003005> "A pH growth preference in which an organism can grow at alkaline pH but does not require it.")
