AnnotationAssertion(Annotation(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000119> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/MICRO_0001557>) Annotation(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000119> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OMP_0005009>) Annotation(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000119> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OMP_0005010>) Annotation(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000119> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OMP_0007009>) Annotation(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000119> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OMP_0007945>) <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <https://w3id.org/metpo/1003007> "A pH growth preference characterized by optimal growth in acidic environments (pH below 5.5) with the capacity to also grow at near-neutral pH values.")
